{"tid":649471,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"觀察條鐵！","createTime":"2018-05-01T15:10:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T15:10:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ec4a9730e8eb288f944d7d8a5b5df8495c321a8c","tid":649471,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:10:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20180501/20377443\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180501%2F20377443&d=mrVId5AQ4OUmPFqh%2F%2F%2B5IHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=7ffa1258\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180501%2F20377443&h=dd88a2b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20180501/20377443</a><br />\n<br />\n觀察條鐵！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180501/large/e8813a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180501%2Flarge%2Fe8813a.jpg&h=6efcac88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n張建宗指，政府調派九唔搭八的高級行政主任去立法會做狗仔隊，不是監察而是觀察議員。林鄭形容「這樣沉悶的工作」，叫觀察？EO入職，工作性質唔係來龍和道觀鳥啊！觀鳥還好些，觀建制議員的鳥？我的媽，這種鳥事，由林鄭一錘定音，張建宗保駕護航，建制議員敲鑼打鼓，一定持之以恆。各位公務員，很快的將來，你也有機會去立法會「觀察」，保安局已經派遣過禁毒處的EO，下一批次，輪到：<br />\n<br />\n路政署主任：觀察哪個建制議員跟泛民「有路」。<br />\n<br />\n警務處警司：退休前去觀察「手臂延伸」效應。<br />\n<br />\n食環署EO：追蹤入廁所，觀察議員便後，有無洗手就入去㩒掣。如有議員以區旗國旗抹手，向西環匯報。<br />\n<br />\n衛生署行政主任：麻疹未在立會傳播前，先杜絕醞釀爆發的雞瘟。立會大樓內，男女廁無限期關閉消毒。強制性「有入、冇出」，建制派想在添美道這個大鳥籠中借尿遁唔投票，殺無赦！（唔聽政府話的議員，妖！殺咗佢有乜唔啱，係咪呀何議員！）  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳也 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"}]}